<li class="u-break-words ps-[2px] hide-loading-dot">Alibaba Cloud: <a node="[object Object]" href="https://home.qwencloud.com/api-keys" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-[var(--text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] cursor-pointer">https://home.qwencloud.com/api-keys</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="u-break-words ps-[2px] hide-loading-dot">
<div class="my-[1px]"><div class="py-[3px] whitespace-pre-wrap u-break-words"><strong>Generate new keys</strong> after revoking</div></div>
</li>
<li class="u-break-words ps-[2px] hide-loading-dot">
<div class="my-[1px]"><div class="py-[3px] whitespace-pre-wrap u-break-words"><strong>Never share API keys in messages</strong> - use environment variables or secure vaults instead</div></div>
</li>
</ol>
<div node="[object Object]" data-hr="true" class="h-[13px] my-[1px] flex items-center"><div class="w-full h-[1px] bg-[var(--border-main)]"></div></div>
<div class="my-[1px]"><div class="py-[3px] whitespace-pre-wrap u-break-words"><strong>Now, let me help you integrate these services properly:</strong></div></div>
<div class="my-[1px]"><div class="py-[3px] whitespace-pre-wrap u-break-words">I can help you set up:</div></div>
