<div class="my-[1px]"><div class="py-[3px] whitespace-pre-wrap u-break-words"><strong>What I'll do:</strong></div></div>
<div class="my-[1px]"><div class="py-[3px] whitespace-pre-wrap u-break-words">I'll update the Universal Agentic Worker to support these providers with <strong>secure environment variable handling</strong> so you never have to paste keys in messages again.</div></div>
<div class="my-[1px]"><div class="py-[3px] whitespace-pre-wrap u-break-words"><strong>Should I proceed with:</strong></div></div>
<ol>
