</ol>
<div class="my-[1px]"><div class="py-[3px] whitespace-pre-wrap u-break-words">And please confirm you've <strong>revoked those compromised keys</strong> before I proceed.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex items-center flex-wrap gap-[12px] min-h-8"><div class="flex items-center gap-[2px]"><div class="flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer rounded-md hover:bg-[var(--fill-tsp-white-light)] size-7"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy size-[16px] text-[var(--icon-tertiary)]" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg></div><span class="inline-flex" aria-expanded="false" aria-haspopup="dialog"><div class="flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer rounded-md hover:bg-[var(--fill-tsp-white-light)] size-7"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" width="16" height="16" color="var(--icon-primary)" class="size-[16px] text-[var(--icon-tertiary)]"><g transform="translate(0.6246 1.3878)"><path d="M13.2622 0.180592C13.5767 -0.0889742 14.0495 -0.0526031 14.3191 0.261891L16.5691 2.88689C16.8241 3.18445 16.8074 3.62784 16.5303 3.90496L14.2803 6.15496C13.9874 6.44785 13.5126 6.44785 13.2197 6.15496C12.9268 5.86207 12.9268 5.3873 13.2197 5.09441L14.9783 3.33513L13.1809 1.23748C12.9113 0.922983 12.9477 0.450159 13.2622 0.180592Z" fill="currentColor"></path><path d="M13.2622 9.78069C13.5767 9.51112 14.0495 9.54749 14.3191 9.86199L16.5691 12.487C16.8241 12.7845 16.8074 13.2279 16.5303 13.5051L14.2803 15.7551C13.9874 16.0479 13.5126 16.0479 13.2197 15.7551C12.9268 15.4622 12.9268 14.9874 13.2197 14.6945L14.9783 12.9352L13.1809 10.8376C12.9113 10.5231 12.9477 10.0503 13.2622 9.78069Z" fill="currentColor"></path><path d="M7.05908 5.44988V10.4501C7.05921