t(.shiki)]:text-[var(--text-primary)] manus-markdown group [&amp;&gt;*:first-child]:mt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:first-child&gt;*:first-child]:pt-0 [&amp;&gt;*:last-child]:mb-0 [&amp;&gt;*:first-child&gt;*:first-child]:pb-0 chat-selection-ask-root"><div class="my-[1px]"><div class="py-[3px] whitespace-pre-wrap u-break-words">Perfect. I'll build a <strong>secure, hidden API key management system</strong> for the Universal Agentic Worker that:</div></div>
<ol>
<li class="u-break-words ps-[2px] hide-loading-dot"><strong>Stores API keys securely</strong> (encrypted, not in code)</li>
<li class="u-break-words ps-[2px] hide-loading-dot"><strong>Hidden settings panel</strong> - accessible but not visible by default</li>
<li class="u-break-words ps-[2px] hide-loading-dot"><strong>Support any LLM provider</strong> - pluggable architecture</li>
<li class="u-break-words ps-[2px] hide-loading-dot"><strong>Environment variable fallback</strong> - keys can come from env vars</li>
<li class="u-break-words ps-[2px] hide-loading-dot"><strong>Secure credential storage</strong> - uses system keyring or encrypted files</li>
<li class="u-break-words ps-[2px] hide-loading-dot"><strong>Web UI, CLI, and Android support</strong> - all platforms</li>
</ol>
<div class="my-[1px]"><div class="py-[3px] whitespace-pre-wrap u-break-words">Let me build this now.</div></div></div><div class="relative w-full rounded-[12px] border-[0.5px] border-[var(--border-dark)] bg-[var(--background-menu-white)] max-w-[480px]"><div class="flex items-center justify-between ps-3 pe-4 pt-3 pb-[12px] gap-[12px] rounded-[12px]"><div class="flex items-center gap-[6px] overflow-hidden"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" class="flex-shrink-0"><path d="M13.3574 13.3291C14.6331 12.6198 15.6295 11.5263 16.1923 10.2181C16.7551 8.90992 16.8528 7.46002 16.4704 6.09308C16.0879 4.72614 15.2466 3.51847 14.0768 2.65719C12.907 1.79591 11.474 1.3291 9.9998 1.3291C8.52566 1.3291 7.09266 1.79591 5.92284 2.65719C4.75303 3.51847 3.91171 4.72614 3.52924 6.09308C3.14677 7.46002 3.2445 8.90992 3.8073 10.2181C4.37009 11.5263 5.36653 12.6198 6.64221 13.3291" stroke="var(--text-tertiary)" stroke-width="1.67" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M11.6998 18.7C10.5696 18.8183 9.43005 18.8183 8.2998 18.7" stroke="var(--text-tertiary)" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M12.1998 16.2C10.746 16.4751 9.25357 16.4751 7.7998 16.2" stroke="var(--text-tertiary)" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.5388 5.5L9.01779 7.195C8.97045 7.24796 8.93807 7.31258 8.92397 7.3822C8.90987 7.45183 8.91457 7.52395 8.93759 7.59116C8.9606 7.65836 9.0011 7.71823 9.05491 7.7646C9.10873 7.81097 9.17392 7.84217 9.24379 7.855L10.7318 8.126C10.8055 8.13937 10.874 8.17318 10.9295 8.22359C10.9849 8.27399 11.0251 8.33896 11.0454 8.41109C11.0658 8.48322 11.0654 8.55961 11.0444 8.63155C11.0235 8.7035 10.9827 8.7681 10.9268 8.818L9.03879 10.5" stroke="var(--text-tertiary)" stroke-width="1.67" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><div class="flex flex-1 min-w-0 gap-[6px]"><p class="leading-[20px] text-[var(--