<span class="line"><span style="color:#E06C75">description</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF">: </span><span style="color:#98C379">Build production-grade agentic AI workers with persistent state, hash-based caching, parallel tool execution, and daemon/interactive modes. Use for creating robust multi-turn LLM agents, automating complex workflows, or developing self-managing AI services inspired by the Deep SSnaHke pattern and Google ADK 2.0 principles.</span></span>
